Primary amyloidosis patients with significant organ dysfunction tolerate 
autologous transplantation after conditioning with single-dose total body 
irradiation alone: a feasibility study.

Blum W(1), Khoury H, Lin HS, Vij R, Goodnough LT, Devine S, Dipersio J, Adkins 
D.

